            </span>
            Publications
        </h2>
        <div class="exhibitionList sp-column2">
            <div class="exhibitionList__item">
                <a href="../learn/publications/catalogues/" class="imageHover zoomCaption">
                    <div class="exhibitionList__img">
                        <figure>
                            <img src="/common/img/contents/learn/img3_01.jpg" alt="" class="imgFit cover">
                        </figure>
                    </div>
                    <div class="exhibitionList__detail">
                        <h3 class="exhibitionList__title">Exhibition Catalogues and Related Publications</h3>
                        <p class="exhibitionList__date">Past and recently published exhibition catalogues and collection catalogues.</p>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="exhibitionList__item">
                <a href="../learn/publications/knm-bulletin/" class="imageHover zoomCaption">
                    <div class="exhibitionList__img">
                        <figure>
                            <img src="/common/img/contents/learn/img3_02.jpg" alt="" class="imgFit cover">
                        </figure>
                    </div>
                    <div class="exhibitionList__detail">
                        <h3 class="exhibitionList__title">The Kyoto National Museum Bulletin</h3>
                        <p class="exhibitionList__date">Kyoto National Museum Bulletin is a Japanese-language publication that contains scholarly articles and research findings of the museum's curators and researchers. It includes abstracts in English for each article.</p>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
            
        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="exhibitionListWarp wallBelt bottomNarrow topNarrow">
        <h2 class="circleIconTitle spBlock" id="Contents04">
            <span class="circleIconTitle__icon">
                <picture>
                    <source media="print, screen and (min-width:768px)" srcset="/common/img/contents/learn/ico_school.svg" />
                    <source media="(max-width:767px)" srcset="/common/img/contents/learn/ico_school_sp.svg" />
                    <img src="/common/img/contents/learn/ico_school_sp.svg" alt="">
                </picture>
            </span>
            Educational Outreach
        </h2>
        <div class="exhibitionList sp-column2">
            <div class="exhibitionList__item">
                <a href="/eng/learn/outreach/school/" class="imageHover zoomCaption">
                    <div class="exhibitionList__img">
                        <figure>
                            <img src="/common/img/contents/learn/img4_01.jpg" alt="" class="imgFit cover">
                        </figure>
                    </div>
                    <div class="exhibitionList__detail">
                        <h3 class="exhibitionList__title">School Programs</h3>
                        <p class="exhibitionList__date">University and graduate student volunteers trained by the Kyoto National Museum as "cultural sommeliers" lead educational programs at Kyoto City public elementary and junior high schools using replicas of important works of art. </p>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>



